h4. Actor:
Agent.

h4. Description:
This is the landing page of "Task Status" Report For *Agent* with search panel on top.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Exchange House|guide:_ShowExchangeHousePlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Click "Report" sub menu from left menu.
* Click "Task Status" link.
* Show Landing Page of "Task Status" Report For *Agent*.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Show for task search(agent)" privilege.

h4. Process:
* Show search panel on top grid.
* Show From date.
* Show To Date.
* [Search By List|guide:_PopulateSearchByList].

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Show landing page of "Task status" Report For *Agent*.
** Reset input form on top to search new Report.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

h4. Related Usecase:
* [Generate "Task Status" Report For "Agent"|guide:ExhGetDetailsByRefOrPinForAgentActionService].

